<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>224</hymn_number>
<key>Bb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Khamhbawi sinah hung tuah, ra bai-bai, Baibal ca nih lam an hmuhsak
 lai, Kanmah lakah ni-hin a dir ko, Dawtnak in an kawh ko.

[C1]
   Kan sualnak lung kha a thlen tikah, Kan i pum i kan i nuam lai ta,
   Bawi Jesuh he kan i pumhnak kha, Vancung khua chung a si.

[V2]
 Bawi Jesuh nih ngakchia rat a duh, Mi lung zapi lawm ko seh atu,
 Nangmah kan thim lai, kan Bawi Jesuh, Rau hlah, atu ra tuah.

[C2]
   Kan sualnak lung kha a thlen tikah, Kan i pum i kan i nuam lai ta,
   Bawi Jesuh he kan i pumhnak kha, Vancung khua chung a si.

[V3]
 Nihin kan sinah Jesuh a um, Pathian nawlbia kha ngai tha te-in, Na
 thei lo maw a chim dawtnak in, Ka fa, na ra lai maw?.

[C3]
   Kan sualnak lung kha a thlen tikah, Kan i pum i kan i nuam lai ta,
   Bawi Jesuh he kan i pumhnak kha, Vancung khua chung a si.</lyrics>
<title>KHAMHBAWI SINAH RA TUAH CH224</title>
</song>